      "comment": "CORNHILL RAVEN (7) was never in contention last time after losing her position early at Bendigo, but prior to that won by 2.25 lengths at Geelong (26.55) beating Punitive in a T3 RSTW on June 13. The form out of her last race has been franked. Can bounce back. MANDOLIN STORM (2) was checked in the run and safely held when sixth (27.01) in a Grade 5 over 460m at Warragul. Has the ability and can atone with the right run. BIG BIG BEAR (5) missed the frame last time out when fifth at Bendigo from Box three (24.42) but draws same box here as latest win. Has a good winning strike rate at this journey. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Can figure in the finish. PAW AMALFI (4) cannot be ruled out.",
